          "text": "For intrastate carriers, Georgia's statutory minimums are $100,000 per person / $300,000 per accident in bodily injury liability. However, most brokers and shippers require $750,000-$1,000,000 regardless of state minimums. Interstate carriers need a minimum of $750,000 filed with FMCSA."
