          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The USDOT and MC numbers come same-day when you apply. But your authority doesn't go active for 21 days minimum. Insurance must be filed within 60 days or your authority gets dismissed. Having an experienced agent like RMS handle filings from Day 1 ensures no deadlines are missed."
